title: Mike Wilson: For the S&P 500, Breaking Out Is Hard to Do
description: On today’s podcast, Chief Investment Officer Mike Wilson says a sustained breakout above 3,000 has eluded the S&P 500. Will the Fed’s potential rate cut be the catalyst?
